        <h2 class="__m-h2">Usage</h2>

        <p class="__m-margin-b">This starter app uses Handlebars as template rendering & Mongoose (MongoDB) for database. You can select what type of
            client connection you want.</p>
            <p>Here a view of the <code class="__c-single">package.json</code> :</p>


        <div class="__c-code-block">
            <code><pre>"dependencies": {
    "body-parser": "^1.19.0",
    "cookie-parser": "~1.4.4",
